msgctxt "sn19.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Okilinīsutta → okilini-supattaṅgārakokiri (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Okilinīsutta "
msgstr "15. A Sweltering Woman "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn19.15:1.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ itthiṃ uppakkaṃ okiliniṃ okiriniṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantiṃ. "
msgstr "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a scorched woman, sooty and sweaty, flying through the air, "

msgctxt "sn19.15:1.2"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … "
msgstr "as she screamed in pain. …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.15:1.3"
msgid "esā, bhikkhave, itthī kaliṅgassa rañño aggamahesī ahosi. "
msgstr "“That woman used to be the king of Kaliṅga’s chief queen. "

msgctxt "sn19.15:1.4"
msgid "Sā issāpakatā sapattiṃ aṅgārakaṭāhena okiri … pe …. "
msgstr "She was of jealous nature, and poured a brazier of hot coals over her co-wife. …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.15:1.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

